{"tid":2103752,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[我係鬥黃分化撚] 身邊有好多自稱係黃但又唔投票嘅人","createTime":"2020-07-11T12:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T05:27:43.000Z","uid":226913,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"333a6043ab251aa74fe097a7b81dd31d1f293491","tid":2103752,"uid":226913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T12:17:02.000Z","msg":"預咗比人屌我鬥黃，但不吐不快<br />\n<br />\n你地話自己係黃<br />\n遊行唔去、和理Shop唔去、文宣唔做、Twitter 戰線唔打<br />\n<br />\n以上我由頭到尾都冇屌過，因為我明大家有家室，可以承受嘅風險唔同，亦冇怪過你地<br />\n但去到尋日我問你地投唔投票，你地話唔知係今日投票<br />\n唔緊要，我咪send哂流程票站位置比你地囉<br />\n跟住你地竟然話要登記身分証資料，驚日後秋後算賬，我就真條忍唔住要屌<br />\n<br />\n投個票有幾撚大風險？連建制派都話唔犯法，你驚乜撚？<br />\n人地出黎參選都未驚，你地投個票竟然話驚？<br />\n<br />\n我屌哂你地老母"},{"pid":"20aec0fc71513675f03fb81aed48d905fb002dd6","tid":2103752,"uid":124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T12:31:24.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />投個票都驚"},{"pid":"19d53d19e687636c7633c758093dd8d80845fd55","tid":2103752,"uid":226913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b82e93d2a54373445a533449c26bbdcb0eb9be","tid":2103752,"uid":284595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T13:31:33.000Z","msg":"驚條L咩 人地跟本無拎你資料 睇下就比番你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1585cb864756cb3e60626b93def9272ab61f8994","tid":2103752,"uid":226913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34b82e93d2a54373445a533449c26bbdcb0eb9be","tid":2103752,"uid":284595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T13:31:33.000Z","msg":"驚條L咩 人地跟本無拎你資料 睇下就比番你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T05:27:43.000Z","msg":"咪就係 <img src=\"/asset